  "name": "Rain of Colours",
  "type": "feat",
  "effects": [],
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><span lang=\"EN\">Your medium is one where you spread your palette to the world. It could be a magical brush, where you paint the air with vibrant flames or freezing ice. It might be a pouch of magical chalk, blown by the wind to bring colorful emotions. Your ephemeral catalyst and catalyst cache could be a palette, or a container for all the different colors you could use for your medium. As your draw, flourish and bring a cascade of colors, your envisioned magic takes shape with the world as your canvas. A painted flame could turn into a launched fireball, or a spray of earthen colors takes life into a wall of stone.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN\">Your key attribute score is Intelligence, and your visionary skill is Crafting. You gain the @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.classes.UBGl2v47K80kpo4A]{Smudge} action.</span></p>"
